I really enjoy working with PyTorch, but I have a feeling the optimizers/schedulers do not have a straight forward implementation. (mostly schedulers though).
Is there a roadmap to create a more unified API for them? Is it something you could use or want help with?

@0phoff could you elaborate on points that could be improved on optimizer? Also, what do you think a more unified API should look like?

